However, a certain number of men are not excluded from this
benediction. The mystery of the resurrection dwells in their souls,
and these are they who have the privilege of being counted among the
number of the sons of God. for they perceive the light which reigns
in the world and which the world sees notï¼š they see it, know it, and
witness it.
